Hey everyone, I've been retrieving feedback/asking NS'ers around, and everyone loves the old t-shirt design (from NS Conference in Amsterdam, 2023). So I did some tests to see how it would look on the hoodies. 
What do you think? Do we want to add the icons as well? 
@undefined could you please share the icons files to test how it would look?

Hey team, we had a first meeting with Justin:
@undefined - Will support with suppliers, demand analysis, polls, sourcing materials
@undefined - Will support with design, sourcing materials/products as well, & content
@undefined - Contact and negotiation with Malaysian suppliers
@undefined  - Is taking care of water bottles with Justin.

Next steps:
(1) I'll send a poll by tomorrow asking for the main products people are interested in (organic shirts, hoodies, caps) and extra items suggestions.
(2) Once we have a clear idea of the products with higher demand, we'll request samples, and start design.
(3) Next Merch meeting this Weds (lvl 13), time tbc

@undefined mentioned she wanted to help with the store as well!

Would be great to get ideas for the store, supply chains, as well as how we can promote them internally. 

We can meet tomorrow afternoon around 12pm on the 13th floor if that works for everyone

@undefined my quick thoughts regarding setting up payments for the cafe/kitchen:

1. To enable card payments: https://www.hitpayapp.com/shopify or something else. to link to the (existing?) shopify store too 

2. to enable stablecoin payments: it'll be good to create a fresh new wallet to receive the payments. And I can help set something up to keep track

Thank you for your suggestions!

Longer term initiatives are fantastic, but as we are iterating daily now, we're looking for a solution which we can implement immediately. 

@electrafrost.btc or anyone else who has ideas which can be implemented immediately please let me know. We can use more than one volunteer for this!
